      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_10" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.223-17</ph> Affirmative Procurement of EPA-designated Items in Service and Construction Contracts.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body"
            outputclass="Body"
            class="- topic/p "
            id="d3367e13">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1094741.dita#i1094741"
                     base="i1094741"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">23.406</xref>(e)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p otherprops="Ctr_SmCaps" outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Affirmative Procurement of EPA-designated Items in Service and Construction Contracts (Aug 2018)</p>
         <ol id="d3349e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3367e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  In the performance of this contract, the Contractor shall make maximum use of products containing recovered materials that are EPA-designated items unless the product cannot be acquired-</p>
               <ol id="d3349e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3367e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Competitively within a timeframe providing for compliance with the contract performance schedule;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3367e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Meeting contract performance requirements; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3367e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        At a reasonable price.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3367e68" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Information about this requirement is available at EPAâ€™s Comprehensive Procurement Guidelines web site, <xref href="https://www.epa.gov/smm/comprehensive-procurement-guideline-cpg-program"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">http://https://www.epa.gov/smm/comprehensive-procurement-guideline-cpg-program</xref>. The list of EPA-designated items is available at <xref href="https://www.epa.gov/smm/comprehensive-procurement-guideline-cpg-program"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">http://https://www.epa.gov/smm/comprehensive-procurement-guideline-cpg-program</xref>.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
